st, and wait for the price of the floor to be raised；\\n\\n3\\\\.Free: Unconditional grabs such as ICP, SOL chains, etc., ETH chain discretionary grabs；\\n\\n4\\\\.Whitelist: grab the popular whitelist, can do meme pictures, water groups, etc；\\n\\n5\\\\.Pay more attention to the big V of the NFT industry and see which projects he pays attention to；\\n\\n6\\\\.Find a few like-minded friends to form a small group；\",\"timestamp\":1634261294,\"title\":\"How to join NFT，profit\"},\"digest\":\"ggSb9cS5b0Na8gLaTFNieyR9idVmvFSSz35VwO78G9k\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf2EB70e0c90CB9C8720CB374a8690cdC63E1680a\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RcLCuDf2jHbWfKGT9oOOdB5QSmI3CLF-I3VvunBbt1k\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"nXCfpsst8pcFhDZ_WCzLBgxCx6XqueM7k4kM_7fl3mI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"JVjbs5X86Jleshq7fXpoONVD1EyuBNo8oR02triu2VPI6fFy-hAh2UIMhF_1tN0uwYUEdixVc3L_P8faYx-Vbw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x56cdca7bb01eee83af95dfe5beda5ef2e70e3a43c8a31500d1315f913ed12ac661cdb34fc8b5990292b6169bef73c66e0c334291ebf0fc3fa3418b60cc5901261c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RcLCuDf2jHbWfKGT9oOOdB5QSmI3CLF-I3VvunBbt1k\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"nXCfpsst8pcFhDZ_WCzLBgxCx6XqueM7k4kM_7fl3mI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ggSb9cS5b0Na8gLaTFNieyR9idVmvFSSz35VwO78G9k\"}"